name: Warmup_Div02_Sub04
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD2S4.CPF,
GmailD2S4.NOME,
GmailD2S4.EMAIL,
GmailD2S4.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S4.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD2S4.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD2S4.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD2S4.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV02_SUB04 GmailD2S4
UNION
